OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with some showery outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain, some of these will be heavy
OL,9,Fat first, gradually easing overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FDull, cool and cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe morning with a few light showers.
OL,13,FSome brighter spells may develop later
OL,14,Fin the day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,17,Fstart Monday with some bright spells,
OL,18,Fthen rain for a time later. Bright
OL,19,Fspells and a few showers through
OL,20,FTuesday and Wednesday. Remaining quite
OL,21,Fcool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
